[b][u][size=14pt]          [color=#AF7817]Technical Specifications:[/color]          [/size][/u][/b]
   [table][tr][td]
   [/td]
   [td]
[center]
2.0 minute block targets

Block rewards in order:
Blocks 1 – 200 = 10,000 GLD
Blocks 201 – 2,200 = 1,000 GLD
Blocks 2,201 – 44,999 = 500 GLD
Starting Block 45,000 rewards drops to 45 GLD
Reward is then reduced each year using the following formula:
50 divided by (1.1 + 0.49*every year thereafter)

Total Premine: Zero (0)
Total Blocks: 26,325,000 (not final)

[b]Total Coins Produced: 123,423,900[/b]

The default ports are 8121 (connect) and 8122 (fson rpc)
[/center]
   [/td]
   [td]
[center]
[b]What makes Goldcoin different?[/b]

[list]
[li]A great name meaning "value" to billions of people Worldwide.[/li]
[li]Unique and innovative 51% attack defense system.[/li]
[li]A genuinely unique coin not just another litecoin clone.[/li]
[li]Newly developed difficulty algorithm "Golden River."[/li]
[li]Total number of coins to be mined 123,423,900.[/li]
[li]Faster transactions than LTC and BTC - 2 minutes.[/li]
[li]Faster difficulty adjustment time - each block.[/li]
[li]Coin generation rules modeled after physical gold.[/li]
[li]Hash algorithm (scrypt) making it ASIC resistant.[/li]
[li]Gradual reduction in block reward creating diminishing coin supply.[/li]
[li]Block reward rules that finally cap supply after 100 years of mining.[/li]
[/list]
[/center]
   [/td][/tr][/table]

[b]Coin Generation:[/b]
Our generation rules condense the entire history of gold from the beginning to the end, when Earth's finite supply is finally exhausted into a scaled and practical 100-year model making them both limited finite resources.

